==Behind the scenes==
The ''[[Living Force Campaign Guide]]'' was written before [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']] established that the Republic did not have a standing military, so it had Colonel Tramsig leading Republic military forces. When AotC came out, it was established that the military units in the Cularin system were instead from a nearby system, Thaere. In the original version, it was clear that the Jir Tramsig was up to ''something'', but it was probably not the apparent expansionist agenda it became under the Thaereian version.

